survey_response.review_text: The services provided are excellent also the doctors are very friendly and understanding .  clinic was very clean and hygienic.
The doctor explained the procedures clearly. They made sure we feel comfortable. There was almost no waiting time.

Well maintained environment, care taking staff and friendly approach towards  patient.Doctor's advice regarding treatment procedure, minimise the cost and step by step treatment are very much appreciated and overall communication regarding appointments, follow-up reminders are quite exemplary.

Actually, I'm not happy with anything that you have mentioned in the above, you may have trained staffs over your clinic,but as a patient what I need is to talk to doctor because I'm already in trauma of extraction of teeth, and the nursing staffs over there is not giving me a satisfying reply, I myself needed to ask what is the problem and all, they just look into my mouth for 2,3 seconds and just said that you need to remove as soon as possible, see this is not the right way of conveying to a patient like me. and I keep on asking questions like is there any other way then removing, or is that safe and how can you confirm that I have infectious tooth and also I'm in pain she didn't even consider it as a matter and asking me for the consultation fee which is a large amount for telling the solution which I already know. So please add nothing in the above list.

A word of appreciation 

I am extremely delighted to give my feedback on my visit to Dr. Mitran's dental clinic as a patient ailing with severe toothache, on 21st June 2022. As I was severely suffering from toothache I could not speak and hence I noted down all my points in a paper and gave it to a team of doctors. I was surprised to see so many doctors in a clinic. They read the paper very patiently and discussed with me under the able stewardship of Dr. Sankar Ram Mithran M. D. S. Then they decided that extraction of tooth is the only way to stop my ache. So they consulted me under the captaincy of Dr. Mithran and when I said ok, one doctor took the job of extracting my tooth. She did it so excellently well, that I didn't feel any pain during the extraction. After half an hour, they discharged me with certain important instructions. To cap those all the doctor who extracted my tooth, on the 3rd day enquired me about my well-being our phone. This follow-up work, no other clinic is doing. It is the patient who has to visit the clinic or hospital for a review meeting. I wish Dr.Mithran, M. D. S. and his team well.

S. Natarajan, 
M. A, B. Sc, M. Ed
Rtd Headmaster .

I wish him all success in growth of hospital.
All the very best 💐🙏🎉
